    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes have softened, reduce the heat to medium, add your <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>, <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong> and <strong>halved</strong> <strong>olives</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>stock</strong> with the <strong>spinach</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until the sauce has thickened and the spinach has wilted</p>",
