    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>orecchiette</strong> through the sauce with your <strong>sun-dried tomato pesto</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) and a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy sundried tomato & olive sauce with fresh orecchiette</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
